Lejog - Day 0:   blog

Initial ride from Penzance to lands end (strava link), then off to the youth hostel. Got lost coming out of the train station and hit a mean hill straight away.

Photos at Lands End, and meet a Scot who had driven down from John O'groats that day. Said he was waiting for a group of 26 to do the downward journey in 24hrs. I'm sure that's nearly 40mph average :s

Chinese take away and several pints have put a shine on the short start.
